OL,6,FParamedics called to Mrs Morgan's
OL,7,FCalder Avenue home in Whitehaven found
OL,8,Fher emaciated, severely malnourished
OL,9,Fand clinically dehydrated.
OL,11,FShe died 10 days later from emaciation
OL,12,Fand neglected infected pressure sores.
OL,14,FAt that time, the retired factory
OL,15,Fworker lived with her husband, Robert
OL,16,FChristopher Morgan, 61, and 53-year-
OL,17,Fold David Alan Holyoak ` her son by
OL,18,Fanother man.
