OL,4,Cwife and mother
OL,6,FMorgan ` known as Chris ` and Holyoak
OL,7,Fdenied manslaughter by gross
OL,8,Fnegligence but were convicted
OL,9,Ffollowing a jury trial.
OL,11,FThe prosecution said they failed to
OL,12,Fprovide her with adequate food and
OL,13,Fwater; failed to ensure she was
OL,14,Fproperly looked after in a safe and
OL,15,Fhygienic home; and failed to call for
OL,16,Fany medical help or other assistance.
