OL,6,FCarlisle Crown Court heard that
OL,7,Fdespite Mrs Morgan's condition
OL,8,Fworsening, Morgan and Holyoak "stood
OL,9,Fby and allowed ` watched ` as she
OL,10,Fdeteriorated".
OL,12,F"From some point between 14 and 28
OL,13,FDecember 2020, onward, Mrs Morgan had
OL,14,Fbeen unable to take care of her own
OL,15,Fbasic human needs," said prosecutor
OL,16,FIain Simkin KC as the pair, of Calder
OL,17,FAvenue, were sentenced on 25 March.
OL,19,FMrs Morgan was also suffering from the
OL,20,Fonset of sepsis up to 48 hours prior
OL,21,Fto her hospitalisation.
