OL,6,F"Such a course of conduct, we say, can
OL,7,Freadily be characterised as a blatant
OL,8,Fdisregard and, given the extended
OL,9,Fperiod whereby the deceased was
OL,10,Fabandoned, it would have been obvious
OL,11,Fto them ` blatant, we say ` that there
OL,12,Fwas a very high risk of death had she
OL,13,Fbeen left in the state that she was."
OL,15,FYet no help was summoned for Mrs
OL,16,FMorgan until 25 January 2021, when her
OL,17,Fhusband dialled first an on-call
OL,18,Fhealth operator and then 999, after
OL,19,Ffinishing a lengthy night shift.
