OL,6,F'Depressed and malnourished'
OL,8,FYet in a text message to a friend, in
OL,9,FOctober 2020, son Holyoak said he
OL,10,Fthought his mother was "depressed and
OL,11,Fmalnourished".
OL,13,F"This sounds like you are watching a
OL,14,Flady die," the friend had responded.
OL,16,FWhen asked under cross-examination by
OL,17,FMr Simkin what provisions there had
OL,18,Fbeen to ensure Mrs Morgan was cared
OL,19,Ffor, Holyoak replied: "I don't
OL,20,Fremember any." He conceded: "I should
OL,21,Fhave done more."
